sentences: Kanae Ito (伊藤 かな恵, Itō Kanae, born November 26, 1986) is a Japanese voice actress and singer from Nagano Prefecture.
After graduating from high school, Ito attended the Amusement Media Academy in 2007.
She was a member of the groups Koetchi (こえっち) and Rirachitchi (りらちっち), before they were disbanded between December 16, 2005 and January 28, 2007.
